OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778249472
OL,3,CAston Villa beat Nottingham Forest as
OL,4,CEurope hears the Midlands roar
OL,6,FAston Villa blew Nottingham Forest
OL,7,Faway in the first all-Midlands
OL,8,FEuropean tie but the atmosphere in
OL,9,Fboth legs of this semi-final was a
OL,10,Fmemorable showcase for Midlands
OL,11,Ffootball.
OL,13,FThe mood was set early for second leg
OL,14,Fas the Villa team bus arrived through
OL,15,Fclaret and blue flare smoke and a wall
OL,16,Fof noise.
OL,18,FThousands of fans were on Trinity Road
OL,19,Fto ensure the players felt their
OL,20,Fbacking from the earliest point of
OL,21,Fthis night.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
