CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778249472
OL,3,CAston Villa beat Nottingham Forest as
OL,4,CEurope hears the Midlands roar
OL,6,FIt was this atmosphere around the
OL,7,Fstadium that started to change my own
OL,8,Fopinion on who I thought would reach
OL,9,FIstanbul.
OL,11,FThe determination and unity around
OL,12,FVilla Park was clear.
OL,14,FThe fans of both these former European
OL,15,FCup winners provided one of the
OL,16,Fbiggest sources of pride.
OL,18,FAfter Forest scored in the first leg
OL,19,Fat the City Ground, it was one of the
OL,20,Floudest atmospheres I've ever heard.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778249472
OL,3,CAston Villa beat Nottingham Forest as
OL,4,CEurope hears the Midlands roar
OL,6,FThe Villa fans' response in Birmingham
OL,7,Fwas emphatic.
OL,9,FIt was difficult for the 2k Forest
OL,10,Ffans to make themselves heard.
OL,12,FBritish fans do not consistently make
OL,13,Fnoise like some European stadiums but
OL,14,Fnowhere are the stands more connected
OL,15,Fto the action on the pitch.
OL,17,FHere, the noise grew and Villa
OL,18,Fattacked.
OL,20,FVilla attacked again and the noise
OL,21,Fgrew louder still.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
