FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778249472
OL,3,CAston Villa beat Nottingham Forest as
OL,4,CEurope hears the Midlands roar
OL,6,FThe roar from the Holte End propelled
OL,7,FUnai Emery's men towards goal.
OL,9,FVilla fans have been quick to mock
OL,10,FForest supporters for perhaps over-
OL,11,Fcelebrating the first leg win.
OL,13,FIt's fair game but football is also
OL,14,Fabout making memories.
OL,16,FPutting aside the fact fireworks are
OL,17,Fset off after every home win, what
OL,18,Fwould Forest fans be left with now if
OL,19,Fthey suppressed their emotions last
OL,20,Fweek?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778249472
OL,3,CAston Villa beat Nottingham Forest as
OL,4,CEurope hears the Midlands roar
OL,6,FIt will hurt to exit Europe without
OL,7,Fthe ultimate success but that night is
OL,8,Fnot suddenly erased from fans'
OL,9,Fcollective memory.
OL,11,FVilla will now head to Istanbul
OL,12,Fexpecting to lift the trophy. No fan I
OL,13,Fspoke to last night thought they
OL,14,Fwouldn't go on to win.
OL,16,FIn any case, this tie was proof that
OL,17,Fthe decades-long duopoly of London and
OL,18,FNorth West success in Europe is being
OL,19,Fbroken.
OL,21,FThe Midlands is back.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
